wiki.content:
"Dakota" is a song by the Welsh band Stereophonics. It was the first single from their fifth studio album Language. Sex. Violence. Other? and was released on February 28, 2005. 
 
 It was the first Stereophonics single to reach #1 on the UK Singles Chart.
 
 "Dakota" is also the soundtrack of EA Sports game FIFA Manager 06.
